<%= render partial: 'form' %>

<%- if @machines -%>
<%= render partial: 'machines/table', locals: {machines: @machines} %>
<%- end -%>

<div class="alert" style="margin-top: 15px">
<h5>Query format</h5>
<p>
Search requests are in the format
<code>name=version</code> where the <code>=version</code> part is optional.
A request <code>openvpn=2.3.11 nmap=7.12</code> would return all machines with openvpn version 2.3.11 and nmap version 7.12 installed.<br/>
Currently only conjunction of search terms is supported, every term stated must be fulfilled.
</p>
</div>

